data.title: #Andrea%20Ferro | femalefrontedbandsconfessions
data.text: Hello, welcome to the Female fronted bands confessions, a blog to which you can submit your confessions about rock or metal bands with a female vocalist. I don't think "Female fronted" is a genre. Confessions can be even mildly related to the topic, just please when expressing criticism, be polite. If you don't want to see people expressing criticism, you can block the tag "Confession criticism" and you'll see only people expressing their positive feelings. Your confessions will stay anonymous. Also, I’d like to emphasize that these confessions aren’t mine and neither are the images I use so all credit to their makers. I hope you will enjoy the blog.
